{
  "stem": "1419.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the MP came through, German MP-- I mean, American MP.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they just looked at us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were dressed maybe different than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they picked us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they, they searched us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they found pictures of-- a friend of mine had pictures from, from concentration camp, from, from crematorium, you know, little tiny pictures.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Somebody must have taken pictures in like a crematorium, I don't know, from Dachau or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took the pictures from us away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had some money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They took the money away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they say, they're fucking Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they gave us back-- and they gave us to the-- to the railroad police, the German railroad police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were with them for quite a few hours, and they released us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They walked away, just like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was the accident-- the incident that I went through.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I couldn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I couldn't defend myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was quite an experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they, they-- I think, how could it be that the Germans were civilized after they went-- what they did to the-- to the-- to the people, to not only the Jews?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I cannot explain it exactly if it was because of that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it's only of, of, of prejudice, of hatred.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know incidents about now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're talking about the history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're talking General Patton, we know about that he-- that he not exactly-- he not-- he didn't favor the, the DPs, the Jewish people in, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what the history tells you now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Jewish people were-- they were confined to certain places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They couldn't-- to the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was not in the DP camps, by the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they were confined to the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
